All rclone backends:

  alias        Alias for a existing remote
  acd          Amazon Drive
  azureblob    Microsoft Azure Blob Storage
  b2           Backblaze B2
  box          Box
  crypt        Encrypt/Decrypt a remote
  cache        Cache a remote
  drive        Google Drive
  dropbox      Dropbox
  ftp          FTP Connection
  gcs          Google Cloud Storage (this is not Google Drive)
  http         http Connection
  swift        Openstack Swift (Rackspace Cloud Files, Memset Memstore, OVH)
  hubic        Hubic
  jottacloud   JottaCloud
  koofr        Koofr
  local        Local Disk
  mega         Mega
  onedrive     Microsoft OneDrive
  opendrive    OpenDrive
  pcloud       Pcloud
  qingstor     QingCloud Object Storage
  s3           Amazon S3 Compliant Storage Provider (AWS, Alibaba, Ceph, Digital Ocean, Dreamhost, IBM COS, Minio, etc)
  sftp         SSH/SFTP Connection
  union        A stackable unification remote, which can appear to merge the contents of several remotes
  webdav       Webdav
  yandex       Yandex Disk

To see more info about a particular backend use:
  rclone help backend <name>
